  "subject": "Temporarily comment-out monitor module build in src/Makefile",
  "commit_message": "Temporarily comment-out monitor module build in src/Makefile\n\nAlso removes 'replace' directives in monitor/go.mod that cause\nthe build to fail with Go 1.14.4\n\nThe CI build currently fails with the change to monitor/go.mod\nthat is why the src/Makefile has the monitor build commented-out.\n\nWhen the monitor build failure is resolved, the commented-out\nmonitor build can be restored.\n\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-1106\nSigned-off-by: Larry Sachs <larry.j.sachs@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ic463129a0a608b4be74245ad4abe89c8c31bfd66\n",
